      <title>贝利的沉默引发英国央行 8 月降息悬念</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-21/bailey-s-silent-treatment-stokes-boe-august-rate-cut-suspense</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国央行行长安德鲁·贝利（Andrew Bailey）已经沉默了两个月，这让每个人都无法猜测利率将何时发生重大变化，也没有太多可参考的信息。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-21/bailey-s-silent-treatment-stokes-boe-august-rate-cut-suspense</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 21 Jul 2024 05:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>韩联社：韩国检察机关就奢侈品包包问题对第一夫人进行调查</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-21/s-korea-prosecutors-question-first-lady-on-luxury-bag-yonhap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据韩联社报道，韩国检察机关首次对总统尹锡烈的妻子进行讯问，指控其收受奢侈手袋礼物和操纵股票。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-21/s-korea-prosecutors-question-first-lady-on-luxury-bag-yonhap</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 21 Jul 2024 02:20:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>哥伦比亚石油公司寻求立法降低租金和电价</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-20/colombian-president-asks-lawmakers-law-change-to-lower-electricity-tariffs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[哥伦比亚总统古斯塔沃·佩特罗表示，哥伦比亚的电价和租金是通货膨胀的主要驱动因素，政府希望立法者修改规范此类成本的立法。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-20/colombian-president-asks-lawmakers-law-change-to-lower-electricity-tariffs</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 20 Jul 2024 23:46:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普粉丝高呼他们希望拜登而不是哈里斯成为 2024 年大选对手</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-20/trump-fans-yell-they-want-biden-not-harris-as-2024-opponent</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普在密歇根集会上对支持者进行了民意调查，询问他们是否希望他与总统乔·拜登或副总统卡马拉·哈里斯竞争。压倒性的嘈杂声音表明他们希望这位 81 岁的总统成为特朗普的对手。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-20/trump-fans-yell-they-want-biden-not-harris-as-2024-opponent</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 20 Jul 2024 23:03:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>工党将与英国养老金主管讨论“大爆炸”改革</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-20/labour-to-discuss-big-bang-reforms-with-uk-pension-chiefs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国新工党政府将于周一会见养老金行业高管，以期促进经济增长并提高储蓄回报。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-20/labour-to-discuss-big-bang-reforms-with-uk-pension-chiefs</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 20 Jul 2024 21:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以色列袭击也门港口城市以回应胡塞无人机袭击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-20/israel-says-it-struck-targets-in-houthi-controlled-red-sea-port</link>
      <description><![CDATA[以色列袭击了胡塞武装控制的红海港口荷台达周围的目标，以报复伊朗支持的武装分子对特拉维夫的无人机袭击，这次袭击造成一名男子死亡，并暴露了以色列防空系统的弱点。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-20/israel-says-it-struck-targets-in-houthi-controlled-red-sea-port</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 20 Jul 2024 16:48:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>俄罗斯协议结束后阿塞拜疆可能通过乌克兰出口天然气</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-20/azerbaijan-may-export-gas-via-ukraine-after-russia-deal-ends</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统伊利哈姆·阿利耶夫表示，乌克兰和欧盟已与阿塞拜疆接洽，希望在与俄罗斯的现有合同于今年年底到期后，通过乌克兰向欧洲供应天然气。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-20/azerbaijan-may-export-gas-via-ukraine-after-russia-deal-ends</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 20 Jul 2024 16:02:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Allstate 和 State Farm 因毛伊岛火灾赔偿 40 亿美元被起诉</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-20/allstate-state-farm-sued-over-4-billion-maui-fire-settlement</link>
      <description><![CDATA[六名毛伊岛山火受害者起诉了包括 State Farm 和 Allstate 在内的一批保险公司，指控他们破坏了他们达成的 40 亿美元索赔和解协议。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-20/allstate-state-farm-sued-over-4-billion-maui-fire-settlement</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 20 Jul 2024 15:32:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>无人机袭击乌克兰电网 俄罗斯机场遭袭</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-20/russian-drones-target-more-ukrainian-power-facilities-overnight</link>
      <description><![CDATA[俄罗斯夜间使用无人机袭击了乌克兰北部和中部的输电设施，造成当地家庭和工业生产者暂时断电。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-20/russian-drones-target-more-ukrainian-power-facilities-overnight</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 20 Jul 2024 09:58:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登密谋挽救许多盟友认为已结束的竞选活动</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-20/biden-plots-to-salvage-campaign-many-allies-believe-already-over</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统乔·拜登本周末与高级政治助手们聚在一起，计划重返竞选之路，为挽救连任做最后的努力——尽管民主党同僚们急切地恳求他下台。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-20/biden-plots-to-salvage-campaign-many-allies-believe-already-over</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 20 Jul 2024 09:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
